OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain or drizzle through
OL,7,Fthe evening. These easing after
OL,8,Fmidnight to become largely dry by
OL,9,Fdawn. Perhaps some clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMostly dry Tuesday morning
OL,13,Fand often cloudy, but some brighter
OL,14,Fspells are possible. Cloud clearing in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon to give longer sunny
OL,16,Fperiods. Very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
